## Notes on document upload:

Creating a document to lectio is split in 2 parts:
- Visit folder where document is to be uploaded, to get VIEWSTATEX
- Upload file using POST request with multipart/form-data
- Apply the upload using another post request

#### Getting VIEWSTATEX:
Visit the folder where we are going to upload the file to:
URL: https://www.lectio.dk/lectio/165/DokumentOversigt.aspx?elevid=31476392835&folderid=S31487886435__
Request Method: GET

Extract the following:
```
<input type="hidden" name="__VIEWSTATEX" id="__VIEWSTATEX" value="">

<input type="hidden" name="__EVENTVALIDATION" id="__EVENTVALIDATION" value="">
```


#### Uploading a document:
To upload the document, we require a VIEWSTATEX key and being authenticated with cookies.
Here are the following important attributes
URL: https://www.lectio.dk/lectio/165/documentchoosercontent.aspx?year=2020&ispublic=0&showcheckbox=1&mode=pickfile
Request Method: POST
content-type: multipart/form-data;

After the upload, a response is sent back. We need a few key things in this response in order to send the following confirmation request for the file. 
```
send.SendMessageToHost({
    "type": "Selected",
    "data": {
        "type": "serializedAnyFileId",
        "serializedId": "DT49742997695",
        "isPublic": true,
        "filename": "EXAMPLE FILE.txt"
    }
}, undefined);
```

#### Applying upload:
URL: https://www.lectio.dk/lectio/165/dokumentrediger.aspx?folderid=S31487886435__
Request Method: POST
content-type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

FORM DATA:

```
time: 0
__EVENTTARGET: m$Content$docChooser
__EVENTARGUMENT: documentId
__SCROLLPOSITION: 
__VIEWSTATEX: ">
<input type="hidden" name="__EVENTVALIDATION" id="__EVENTVALIDATION" value="
__VIEWSTATEY_KEY:

```
